race.description: Allure Lash & Beauty Bar Mdn Plate
race.comment: EXTRA HANDS (8) has changed yards on a 13-day return and peaks off three placings. Got to within 1.7L here last time, and the in-form Boudvillian replaces McDougall. Finds the right race and will be hard to beat. HIGH COUNTRY STAR (4) found one much too good here on debut but covered the others and he will be better for the outing. Keeps the handy 2kg claim and can make the finish with average luck in the run. RAVENS GLOW (12) raced at Echuca on debut and looked a run short. She can improve into the money with that under the saddle. McDougall sticks with the Scott-trained SOOTY AND SWEEP (5) and we are likely to see more from him at his second start.
